  "title": "Talent Acquisition (Recruitment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic Salary $2500 to $3500</p></li><li><p><strong>Uncapped Monthly Commission</strong></p></li><li><p>Structured<strong> training and mentorship</strong></p></li><li><p>Fast-track career progression to <strong>Team Lead / Manager</strong></p></li><li><p>Exposure across <strong>multiple industries (F&B, Retail, Logistics, Engineering, Healthcare, etc.)</strong></p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Good Company Benefits<strong> - Annual Leave, Festive Leave, Birthday Leave, Company Trip</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manage full-cycle recruitment: sourcing, screening, interviewing, and shortlisting candidates</p></li><li><p>Work closely with the Business Development Team to understand client's hiring needs and requirements</p></li><li><p>Drive sales results by matching candidates effectively and closing placements</p></li><li><p>Handle job postings, candidate pipelines, and interview coordination</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate records in the CRM</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Sales-driven personality</strong> with strong motivation to hit targets</p></li><li><p>Enjoys speaking to people, relationship building, and closing deals</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>High energy, proactive, and resilient</p></li><li><p>No experience needed — <strong>training is provided</strong></p></li><li><p>Candidates with prior <strong>sales, recruitment, telesales, customer-facing</strong> experience are welcome<br /><br /><strong>📌 Interview on 7 February 2026 | Immediate Hiring Opportunity</strong></p><p>Shortlisted candidates may receive <strong>on-the-spot offers</strong></p></li></ul><p>Applicants who possess relevant experience for the above responsibilities are most welcome to apply. If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities.</p><p>Please submit your updated resume in MS Words format by using the <strong>APPLY NOW BUTTON.</strong></p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by the company relating to this job application.</p><p>https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf</p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.<br /><br /><strong>Yong Jia Wen</strong></p><p><strong>Registration Number: R25146805</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No: 13C6730 (MCI Consulting Pte Ltd)</strong></p>",
